&lt;p&gt;At the foot of majestic Emei Mountain, Anantara Emei Resort is the first international hotel in this breathtaking corner of southwest China. Relax at the outdoor pool beside a beautiful lake and indulge in revitalising Anantara Spa journeys. Dine at the finest Chinese restaurant in Emei, where regional specialties include renowned Sichuan and Cantonese cuisine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beyond our oriental hideaway&amp;#8217;s unique appeal, the resort is surrounded by a UNESCO World Heritage Site, providing a gateway to stunning landscapes and historic attractions of rich cultural diversity. Explore one of China&amp;#8217;s four sacred Buddhist Mountains, where pilgrims climb to visit the seventy-six Buddhist monasteries that grace its path to the peak.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We invite you to enjoy these additional offers:&lt;br /&gt;
